  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\" property=\"schema:text\"><p><strong>Presented by Milliman</strong></p><p><span>High inflation and interest rates, geopolitical conflict, and new solvency regulations contributed to a recent global slowdown in health and life insurance mergers and acquisitions. Milliman’s annual report looks at worldwide M&amp;A activity, breaks down top deals by country, and projects future market conditions. </span></p><p><a href=\"https://www.milliman.com/mareport\"><em><span><strong>Read the full report &gt; </strong></span></em></a></p><p> </p></div></body></html>",
